      propertyPath: 'storyArt.Array.data[21]'
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: -8575487910126867567, guid: 1137a23b9808ddb42bd4b52c152f3f6c, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: 'It is done.\n\n[Press X key to continue]'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: This awful tradition of stripping our free will. It is over.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: All of the friends I gathered in my quest have transformed back into
        their creature forms.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: However, the weapon forms they previously were remained as inanimate
        objects, free for me to use at any time.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: '"Great work, green guy. Looks like this is where we all part ways."
        Erica stated.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: '"ALL of us? You don''t mean you and I are parting ways too, right?!"
        Brad asked in panic.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: '"Of course I mean that too, you idiot. Listen. The next time you get
        into a serious relationship, don''t go cheating on them." Erica answered.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[7]'
      value: '"And don''t go making the excuse that your brain wasn''t in the right
        place. It proves you are not ready for serious commitment." Erica pointed
        out.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[8]'
      value: With that, we watched Erica walk into the distance.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[9]'
      value: '"I am free to go back to guiding the young ones to a better future.
        Many blessings to you on your future endeavors, green one." Wendy said.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[10]'
      value: Wendy too made her departure. I turned to Charles, who had been kneeling
        on the ground in sorrow.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[11]'
      value: '"... Charles? Are you okay?" I asked.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[12]'
      value: '"You got rid of the one person who made me feel like I belonged...
        how can I possibly be okay?!?!" Charles exclaimed.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[13]'
      value: '"Your sense of belonging is not tied to a specific person, Charles.
        It is tied to the way you carry yourself, tied to who you are." I said.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[14]'
      value: '"I don''t know who I am, though!! I... I need to take some time to
        discover myself..." Charles replied.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[15]'
      value: '"However long it takes, old friend. Know that you can come to me for
        anything anytime." I concluded.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[16]'
      value: Charles walked off. The only weapon... I mean, person... left with me
        is Brad.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[17]'
      value: '"Erica is right, Brad. You''re not ready for serious commitment yet."
        I told Brad.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[18]'
      value: '"I know... I guess it''s time for me to learn." Brad stated sadly.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[19]'
      value: '"Why don''t you tag along with me? Maybe you aren''t a committed boyfriend
        today, but I can help you start by teaching you how to be a committed friend."
        I offered.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[20]'
      value: '"That would be swell, Fern!! What are we waiting for?!?!" Brad said
        eagerly.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4496982304778883468, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'storyLines.Array.data[21]'
      value: And thus was the end of...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4788537577470390567, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: ExitDoor (1)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    m_RemovedComponents: []
    m_RemovedGameObjects: []
    m_AddedGameObjects: []
    m_AddedComponents: []
  m_SourcePrefab: {fileID: 100100000, guid: 667b2064d90a8894b8cb1bc849e7e071, type: 3}
